
### Sign Up
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "nguyenhung",
    "email": "nguyenhung@gmail.com",
    "password": "abcd12345"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "nguyenhung@gmail.com",
    "password": "abcd12345"
}

###

### Logout (Single Device)
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/auth/logout
x-refresh-token: YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Logout All Devices
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/auth/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/auth/refresh-token
x-refresh-token: YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

###

### ===================== PRODUCT ===================== ###

### Create Product - Electronics
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/product
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "product_name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
    "product_thump": "https://example.com/iphone15.jpg",
    "product_description": "Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max 256GB - Titanium Blue",
    "product_price": 1199,
    "product_quantity": 100,
    "product_type": "Electronics",
    "product_attribute": {
        "brand": "Apple",
        "size": "6.7 inch",
        "material": "Titanium"
    }
}

###

### Create Product - Clothing
POST http://localhost:8386/api/v1/product
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "product_name": "Nike Air Max T-Shirt",
    "product_thump": "https://example.com/nike-tshirt.jpg",
    "product_description": "Nike Air Max Cotton T-Shirt - Black",
    "product_price": 49,
    "product_quantity": 200,
    "product_type": "Clothing",
    "product_attribute": {
        "brand": "Nike",
        "size": "L",
        "material": "Cotton"
    }
}
